import { Container, Navbar, Nav } from "react-bootstrap";
import { Router, Switch, Link } from "react-router-dom";
import App from "./App";

function NavigationBar() {
    return (
    <Router>
        <Navbar bg="dark" variant="dark">
            <Container fluid>
            <Nav.Link as={Link} to={"Films"}>Home</Nav.Link>
            <Nav.Link as={Link} to={"Films"}>Link</Nav.Link>
            </Container>
        </Navbar>

        <Switch>
            <Route exact path="/">
                <App />
            </Route>
            <Route path="/blogs">
            <Blogs />
            </Route>
            <Route path="/contact">
            <Contact />
            </Route>
        </Switch>
    </Router>
    )
}

export default NavigationBar
